tip.text: The Mini Mushroom Melts are a hidden gem in the menu. If you have space for starters, this is the one to get!
Ordered the ocean linguine after looking through the tips here and it really is one of the best pasta dish I have had.
Don't leave this place with out trying their TIT Honey Toast! Good for two and a great way to end your meal!
